{"body": "I'm not a fan of this feature because I don't think a lot of applications will get advantages of it. Also the implementation is so simple that you can add in your application.\r\n\r\nThe inflector can return some false positive results and this feature will break, leading more pull requests \"fixing\" the inflectors.\r\n\r\nThat said I'm closing this one.\r\n\r\nThank you so much for the contribution.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/9851543", "created_at": "2012-10-28T22:20:56Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6802#issuecomment-9851543", "updated_at": "2012-10-28T22:20:56Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6802, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e2563bd354364b900ddd5"}, "id": 9851543, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6802"}
